cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this work, please cite it as below."
title: "Bias: Probing Caste Bias in Large Language Models"
author:
    Name: "Gagan A Nair"
date-released: 2026-07-18
url: "https://github.com/GAGANANAIR/Bias"
keywords:
  - mechanistic-interpretability
  - sparse-autoencoders
  - llm-bias
  - caste-bias
  - ai-safety
license: MIT
abstract: >
  A research project investigating caste bias in Large Language Models
  (Gemma 2B, Gemma 9B, Llama 3.1 8B) using Sparse Autoencoders and
  circuit tracing via Neuronpedia. Probes model completions for
  Indian first name + surname combinations to surface occupation-prestige
  bias patterns linked to caste identity.
